unk_c820299.value:
-- Re-getting actors in this group in case any have turned off after 
-- spawning their max lifetime monsters. Otherwise we get a nil error.
tWave01Spawners = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Crossway_S04_MusicBoxEvent_Wave01Spawners")

for i, Spawner in ipairs(tWave01Spawners) do
	Hydra.ActorDisable(Spawner)
end
